OL,3,CAlternative healer to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of woman at slap workshop
OL,6,FAn alternative healer who failed to
OL,7,Fget medical help for a 71-year-old
OL,8,Fdiabetic woman who died after she
OL,9,Fstopped taking insulin at his slapping
OL,10,Ftherapy workshop is due to be
OL,11,Fsentenced for manslaughter.
OL,13,FDanielle Carr-Gomm died in October
OL,14,F2016 while taking part in the Paida
OL,15,FLajin therapy event, which sees
OL,16,Fpatients being slapped or slapping
OL,17,Fthemselves repeatedly.
