OL,3,CAlternative healer to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of woman at slap workshop
OL,6,FHongchi Xiao, of Cloudbreak,
OL,7,FCalifornia, was convicted by a jury at
OL,8,FWinchester Crown Court of the
OL,9,Fmanslaughter by gross negligence of
OL,10,FMrs Carr-Gomm, from Lewes, East
OL,11,FSussex, in July.
OL,13,FThe 61-year-old was extradited for the
OL,14,Ftrial from Australia, where he had
OL,15,Fpreviously been prosecuted over the
OL,16,Fdeath of a six-year-old boy who also
OL,17,Fdied after his parents withdrew his
OL,18,Finsulin medication after attending the
OL,19,Fdefendant's workshop in Sydney.
