OL,3,CAlternative healer to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of woman at slap workshop
OL,6,FThe trial heard that Mrs Carr-Gomm,
OL,7,Fwho was diagnosed with Type 1 diabetes
OL,8,Fin 1999, was left "howling in pain" as
OL,9,Fshe became seriously ill before she
OL,10,Fdied on the fourth day of the workshop
OL,11,Fat Cleeve House in Wiltshire.
OL,13,FProsecutor Duncan Atkinson KC
OL,14,Fpreviously told the court that Mrs
OL,15,FCarr-Gomm had sought alternatives to
OL,16,Fher insulin medication for type 1
OL,17,Fdiabetes because of her vegetarianism
OL,18,Fand fear of needles.
