OL,3,CAlternative healer to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of woman at slap workshop
OL,6,FShe had first joined a Paida Lajin
OL,7,Fworkshop, which means "slap and
OL,8,Fstretch", run by the defendant in
OL,9,FBulgaria in July 2016.
OL,11,FMrs Carr-Gomm became seriously ill
OL,12,Fafter stopping her insulin medicine
OL,13,Fbefore she restarted and subsequently
OL,14,Frecovered.
OL,16,FThe jury had heard how Xiao said "well
OL,17,Fdone" to Mrs Carr-Gomm, after she told
OL,18,Fthe group she had stopped taking her
OL,19,Finsulin at the week-long retreat, and
OL,20,Fshe became seriously ill.
