OL,3,CAlternative healer to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of woman at slap workshop
OL,6,FMr Atkinson described how the
OL,7,Fdefendant failed to get medical help
OL,8,Ffor Mrs Carr-Gomm before she died in
OL,9,Fthe early hours of the fourth day.
OL,11,FHe said that Xiao had been an
OL,12,F"exponent" of Paida Lajin for 10 years
OL,13,Fand had written a book on it.
OL,15,FMr Atkinson said: "It is said to be a
OL,16,Fmethod of self-healing in which
OL,17,F'poisonous waste' is expelled from the
OL,18,Fbody through patting and slapping
OL,19,Fparts of the body."
