OL,3,CAlternative healer to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of woman at slap workshop
OL,6,FHe added: "He does not have medical
OL,7,Fqualifications or training."
OL,9,FThe prosecutor said the defendant also
OL,10,Fwrote in the book that "doctors are
OL,11,Fbrainwashed by drug producers to act
OL,12,Fas salespersons for their drugs".
OL,14,FGiving evidence during the trial, Xiao
OL,15,Fsaid he would "never" persuade someone
OL,16,Fwho needed insulin not to take it,
OL,17,Fadding that insulin is "useful".
