OL,6,FThe court heard that Mrs Carr-Gomm had
OL,7,Fprovided a testimonial for Xiao,
OL,8,Fdescribing him as a "messenger sent by
OL,9,FGod" who was "starting a revolution to
OL,10,Fput the power back in the hands of the
OL,11,Fpeople to cure themselves and to
OL,12,Fchange the whole system of healthcare".
OL,14,FHe is due to be sentenced on Friday at
OL,15,FWinchester Crown Court.
